                Sprint Retrospective
            </div>

            <h1>
                Retrospective Board
            </h1>

            <p>
                Analise a Sprint, organize feedbacks e gere insights inteligentes com IA.
            </p>

        </div>

        <div class="retro-header-right">

            <div class="field-group">

                <label>Sprint</label>

                <select id="cmbSprint"
                        onchange="carregarSprint(this.value)">
                    <option value="">
